00063 
00064         // UNITS IN INPUT FILES
00065         // ... Always use atomic units
00066         // ... ... Positions in a0 (bohr)
00067         // ... ... Multipole moment of rank k in e(a0)**k
00068         // ... ... Dipole polarizability in A³ (Angstrom cubed)
00069 
00070         // UNITS USED INTERNALLY
00071         // ... Use nm instead of a0 and A
00072         // ... ... Positions in nm
00073         // ... ... Multipole moment of rank k in e(nm)**k
00074         // ... ... Dipole polarizability in nm³
00075 
00076         // CONVERSION FACTORS
00077         // ... Electric field (N/C) = Electric field (int)
00078         //                          * 1/4PiEps0(SI) * e * 1e+18
00079         // ... Energy (eV) = Energy (int) * 1/4PiEps0(SI) * e * 1e+09
00080         //
00081         // ... Potential (V) = Potential(int) * 1/4PiEps0(SI) * e * 1e+0.9
00082 
00083         inline void Field_AT_DUE(PolarSite &pol1, PolarSite &pol2);
